item.description:
Genre: DANCE POP/EDM/DUBSTEP/LATIN

Catarsis (2013) it’s mexican popstar Belinda’s fourth solo album, it reached #2 on Billboard Latin Albums & topped the charts in Mexico, Argentina, Denmark, Spain & Italy

the 2nd single “En la Obscuridad” (At the Dark) won a VEVO award for surpassing 200 million views on YouTube, and reached high positions in Latin America, Spain, France, South Korea & Slovakia
